extendedInfo.description: Come join us to celebrate the 2012 SVU Annual ConferenceHeld in conjunction with the Society for Vascular Surgery (SVS) at the 2012 Vascular Annual Meeting (VAM), the SVU Annual Conference brings vascular technologists/sonographers, vascular physicians, and vascular lab directors to one exhibit hall to experience new technologies, learn the latest scientific research, and network with other vascular ultrasound professionals.
